msgctxt "an5.48:4.5"
msgid ""
"So jarādhamme jiṇṇe na socati na kilamati na paridevati, na urattāḷiṃ "
"kandati, na sammohaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"And so, when someone liable to old age grows old, they don’t sorrow and pine "
